  <brief_title>Maximal Strength Training in Patients Undergoing Total Hip Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Maximal Strength Training in Patients Undergoing Total Hip Arthroplasty: Implementing Evidence Based Rehabilitation Into Clinical Practice, and the Influence of Supervised Training</official_title>
